        <p><b>15. <i>EXECUTIVE COMPENSATION AND FIRST-TIER SUBCONTRACT AWARDS REPORTING (<a href='https://www.acquisition.gov/far/current/html/52_200_206.html#wp1137568'>FAR 52-204-10</a>)</i></b></p>

        <p>Does your firm file periodic reports on executive compensation under Section 13(a) or 15(d) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (15 U.S.C. 78m(a), 78o(d)) or Section 6104 of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986?</p>
                    
