            <b style ="margin-left:20px"><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox59/> NO </b>
        </p>

        <p><b><i style="color:red;"><u>If Item B. is YES, please complete Exhibit I</u> for each fee, commission, and political contribution, using additional sheets as necessary, referencing the Sales Order/Contract Number at issue, and numbering each successive sheet X of X accordingly.</i></b></p>
    
    </div>

